        the probability density function:

        >>> import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
        >>> count, bins, ignored = plt.hist(s, 30, density=True)
        >>> plt.plot(bins, (1/beta)*np.exp(-(bins - mu)/beta)
        ...          * np.exp( -np.exp( -(bins - mu) /beta) ),
        ...          linewidth=2, color='r')
        >>> plt.show()

