        the probability density function:

        >>> import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
        >>> from scipy import special

        Truncate s values at 50 so plot is interesting:

        >>> count, bins, ignored = plt.hist(s[s<50], 50, density=True)
        >>> x = np.arange(1., 50.)
